703122f-a.folder: Bay 11th Street & Cropsey Avenue, Brooklyn, NY

703889f-b.text:
Cropsey Ave., south side, opposite Bay 11th Street, showing the Benmnett homestead, also known as the Cortelyou house. In 1916 it was accuired by the Millrose Athletic Association for its Country home. Bay 11th Street, terminated at Cropsey Ave. in 1923; hovever the City has condemned this house, and is to continue Bay 11th Street
to Warehouse Ave., an Gwavesend Bay.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
The same, showing the south side of the house.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
The same, showing an easterly view.
April 1923.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
